{
  "stem": "27129.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We heard that they're gonna put a ring around Warsaw, and there's going to be a big fight there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So why should we be right in the middle?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we waited overnight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the meantime, there was shooting between the Polish armies and the Germans, which the Polish wanted to go-- go through, you know, [INAUDIBLE] into Warsaw by-- by daylight.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were in a ho-- in a house over night, by some people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They told us to get out of town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we figured, my brother and I, where there to go?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Go farther east or go back home?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because the Germans are here anyway, so there is no other place to go like home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because there's no better place like home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was a great disappointment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The closer we got to home, you know, they were looking for Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's all they had in mind, you know, Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they put us to clean up those bomb-- bombed home-- houses, you know, that they bombed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And little by little, you know, they made our way-- we made our way through to the city, to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we got pretty scared, you know, because they were shooting people on the way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were holding people, like in camps without giving them food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we tried to avoid the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We used to go through-- through-- through forest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, we didn't go with the main-- the main streets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And finally we made our way home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we came home, it was a terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they passed all kinds of law-- laws against Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Jews are not supposed to walk on sidewalks, only on the pavement.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, and if you didn't, they beat you up.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
